  [ Jonathan Ernst ]
  * Virtualbox should go in Accessories, not in System tools (LP: #288590) 

  [ Daniel Hahler ]
  * New upstream version (LP: #288957)
    - Updated debian/patches/09-initscript.dpatch (one hunk rejected/obsolete)
